sequenceDiagram
    actor C as Candidate
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant GW as API Gateway WebSocket
    participant PIPE as Pipecat
    participant STT as Deepgram STT
    participant IV as Interviewer Agent (Claude)
    participant EV as Evaluator Agent (Claude)
    participant TTS as ElevenLabs TTS
    participant AV as Tavus Avatar

    Note over IV: Holds live state + QuestionPlan

    IV->>TTS: Question text
    TTS->>AV: Audio stream
    AV-->>FE: Lip-synced video + audio
    FE-->>C: Interviewer asks the question

    C->>FE: Speaks answer (mic)
    FE->>GW: Audio stream
    GW->>PIPE: Audio
    PIPE->>STT: Stream
    STT-->>PIPE: Final transcript
    PIPE->>IV: Candidate answer transcript
    IV->>IV: Decide - follow up / push back / move on

    alt Answer vague or unproven
        IV->>TTS: Probing follow-up (why / how exactly?)
        TTS->>AV: Audio
        AV-->>FE: Follow-up delivered
        Note over C,IV: Loop until concrete or max follow-ups hit
    else Answer concrete
        IV->>EV: Final answer + question context
        EV->>EV: Score rubric + wouldSurviveRealInterview
        EV-->>IV: AnswerEvaluation (persisted)
        IV->>IV: Advance to next question
    end
